{"tid":1844152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Condom於雍盛苑屋苑內駐守，有人於上空放煙花。","createTime":"2020-01-26T13:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:33:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"80046dc5c6fdaf03a9732ee2d8457029055d238a","tid":1844152,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/83322031_2808193522599583_1894878938941882368_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ohc=jQaV24CYz00AX9FrkV5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=8eceb8ecd110438a59c7e82a4b5420c1&amp;oe=5EC89781\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F83322031_2808193522599583_1894878938941882368_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ohc%3DjQaV24CYz00AX9FrkV5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D8eceb8ecd110438a59c7e82a4b5420c1%26oe%3D5EC89781&h=9ca84cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩又係綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2808193519266250/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2808193519266250%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=456317e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2808193519266250/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a3f5af450cb32fe91b012bebc3c8a98357fa68f3","tid":1844152,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"c0610f7b68906a9601aaac35cca0495d7baf6022","tid":1844152,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"fb014b11190fe7903484d7e75d441dfd446c35fc","tid":1844152,"uid":270905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"貼相驚死啲popo check 唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8903bd238ef98845630c0fe4778c59820612a47","tid":1844152,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"勇武派 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"2963b1a681247ed9a0b67fb480d69df3dcf558ea","tid":1844152,"uid":134744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"ip都唔洗check"},{"pid":"b6359fe25d07767a02958433f1c1ba3c3729e977","tid":1844152,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"4b61f9dcc6cf275b11bf8e53b34d3c79fb930934","tid":1844152,"uid":318284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1